      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im having a weird issue with my sourdough starter. even though i keep the temp stable at like 75f, the activity is super inconsistent. sometimes it's really active and other times it just sits there. can u explain what's actually going on with the yeast and bacteria interaction that would cause that kind of volatility?",
